title: New: GEO – For You
body:
Was very into Good Morning, the debut track from LA’s **GEO** which dropped a month or so back.

Following it up with the equally as slick, _For You_, it’s just the right kind of ‘vibey’ with a soulful tinge creeping in really allows it to develop it’s own unique personality. Check it out below.
